@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Delivered
Delivered --> Cancelled : process
Cancelled --> OnHold : cancel
Cancelled : entry / log service
OnHold --> Processing : cancel
Processing --> Rejected : reject
Processing : entry / log service
Rejected --> Delivered : revert
Rejected --> [*]
@enduml